Michelle Clunie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michelle_Clunie 0 Michelle Renee Clunie (born November 7, 1969) is an American actress. She is perhaps best known for her roles as Melanie Marcus on Showtime's critically acclaimed series Queer as Folk and as Ellen Beals on Make It or Break It. She is currently a star on MTV’s Teen Wolf as Mrs. Finch. Michelle_Renee_Clunie ( born November_7_,_1969 ) is an_American_actress .
